{"id": "art-366", "label": "Art. 366", "title": "Art. 366: Participarea persoanei vătămate şi a altor subiecţi procesuali la judecată şi drepturile acestora", "slug": "art-366", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_384768428\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1784\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_384768428\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 366:\nParticiparea persoanei v&#259;t&#259;mate &#351;i a altor subiec&#355;i\nprocesuali la judecat&#259; &#351;i drepturile acestora </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1318548921\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1783\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1318548921\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Persoana v&#259;t&#259;mat&#259; poate fi\nreprezentat&#259; de avocat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1417813457\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1782\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1417813457\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Persoana v&#259;t&#259;mat&#259; poate formula cereri,\nridica excep&#355;ii &#351;i pune concluzii în latura penal&#259; a cauzei.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1303316466\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1781\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1303316466\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Persoanele ale c&#259;ror bunuri sunt supuse\nconfisc&#259;rii pot fi reprezentate de avocat &#351;i pot formula cereri,\nridica excep&#355;ii &#351;i pune concluzii cu privire la m&#259;sura\nconfisc&#259;rii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}